---
title: Asian Chicken, Tofu & Asparagus Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice & Sweet Chilli Mayo
description: We’re stirring and frying these soft little tofu cubes in a lavish dark sauce. Bring out those garlic aromatics by cooking it into the greens and the rice. What tofu stir-fry would be complete without a dollop of a sriracha mayo to smother over everything. It’s a gold star from us!

